---
description: "Common preferences"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Always start Cursor in plan mode.
- This project configures Karabiner Elements.
- The Karabiner configuration is intended to be functionally similar to my ZMK keymap configuration. 
    - My ZMK keymap configuration in located at https://github.com/KeyboardHoarders/zmk-config-corne
    - locally in ../keyboardhoarders-zmk-config-corne
- Always execute ./build.sh --install after changes.
- Equivalent changes need to be applied to multiple files so that the files  can be enabled an disabled independently.
- Do not extract rules into separate files unless necessary.
